### Verified Available Data Sources (updated)
- **Wang DLPFC snRNA-seq (GSE311334)**: PUBLIC. 9 samples (5 TD, 4 NT), counts matrix + metadata. Developer task #1412.
- **Grotzinger CDG3 factor GWAS**: On figshare (DOI:10.6084/m9.figshare.30359017), listed as CDG2025 on PGC. Contents not yet verified. Developer task #1413.
- **Ding et al. BG epigenomic (PMC12919054)**: PEER-REVIEWED. 261K cells, 8 subregions. Data on NeMO (nemo:dat-4j3fen2). Portal: basalganglia.epigenomes.net. Developer task #1414.
- **PsychENCODE Hi-C**: NeuN+/NeuN- DLPFC chromatin loops on Synapse. Developer task #1415.
- **HMBA BG Atlas**: ~5.4M cells on AWS S3 (no login). abc_atlas_access Python API. Developer task #1416.
- **GTEx v8 brain eQTL**: Confirmed open access. Developer task #1283.
- **LD reference panel**: All URLs verified. Developer task #1284.
- **OCD/TS 2019 GWAS**: Available on figshare (DOI:10.6084/m9.figshare.14671983).

